title: Coming Soon! ARBORA - Palo Alto, A Luxury Boutique Apartment Community
posting_body: ['Welcome to Arbora', 'Palo Alto’s most desirable collection of new homes.', 'Arbora offers a boutique collection of 19 brand-new residences nestled on a tranquil street in the heart of downtown Palo Alto.', 'Walk to University Avenue, Stanford, Cal Train, or Whole Foods, enjoying a vibrant dining and shopping scene.', 'Or relax and recharge at home, enjoying skyline views from the trellised rooftop deck with a dining area, lounges, fire pit, and outdoor kitchen.', 'Each residence has been uniquely designed to maximize livability, carefully considering light, space, and experience.', 'With floor-to-ceiling windows, hardwood floors, soaring ceilings, and sophisticated finishes, the vibrancy of downtown living now meets the beauty of modern design.', 'We invite you to enjoy elegant architecture, unparalleled convenience, and curated amenities at Arbora.', 'Call to speak with our leasing team today!', 'Amenities Include:', 'Calcatta quartz countertops', 'Lush landscaped interior courtyard', 'Over 10 ft. ceilings', 'Fully-integrated resident app', 'Bike storage', 'Bike repair station', 'Select residences with private terraces', 'Outdoor kitchen and dining', 'Fisher Paykel refrigerator', 'Soaking tub', 'Fully furnished homes upon request', 'Solid wood doors', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Check out the virtual tour: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up-to-date information.']
